            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5046071/">【豆总摘】大纲和重点──看完不用看书了</a></h2>

                <div id="review_5046071_short" class="review-short" data-rid="5046071">
                    <div class="short-content">

